title: - New: YesNoDialogs for Create/Restore DB, Create/Restore Thumb Images, and Relink.
message:
- New: YesNoDialogs for Create/Restore DB, Create/Restore Thumb Images, and Relink.
  (These are potential big jobs which takes time/resource, and can't be stopped/cancelled atm
  There are instances that a user might mistakenly clicking/tapping the option and finds himself
  failing to reverse the action, leading him to either force stopping the app which might just
  do wonders to the app)
- New: Stop Relinking On Click/Tap, also with YesNoDialog for Relink Stop Option.
  (Review first, but as I saw it, it is rather safe to simply stop it, any error created by
  stopping the task prematurely can be fixed by simply rerunning the task, unfortunately,
  NO RESUME SUPPORT atm.)
- Very Minor strings.xml correction.
